one knows more of magic than that Erudite.'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:56:52 2000] Granaut says, 'Al'Kabor..'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:56:55 2000] Thubr Axebringer says, 'Even he could nae trace where th' Iksar had gone.'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:56:55 2000] Guard Andile says 'The Iksar are a race of lizard men.  They are unlike those known to inhabit the Homelands.  The Iksar are much more humanoid and much more intelligent.  It is said they live within a great city which some call [New Sebilis].  We have fought with them often during patrols into the jungles and swamps. <br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:57:03 2000] Thubr Axebringer bonks Guard Andile on the head!<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:57:22 2000] Thubr Axebringer says, 'Aye, that's th' <br>tale.'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:57:23 2000] Zeyk says, 'if they set foot on Tunare's land, I shall find them'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:57:37 2000] Granaut says, 'Interesting..'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:57:41 2000] Domia wonders if Guard Andile has been in the Ale......<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:58:04 2000] You say, 'Does the king have further plans?'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:58:10 2000] Thubr Axebringer says, 'We've looked all across Kunark... and we've nae found a thing.'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:58:27 2000] Thubr Axebringer says, 'Th' King told us t' go find her.  His concentrations are mainly here.'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:58:45 2000] Thubr Axebringer says, 'As for what ye can do... keep yer eyes an' ears open fer anythin' suspicious.'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:58:55 2000] Caylid nods at Thubr Axebringer.<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:59:18 2000] Thubr Axebringer says, 'My plans are t' keep lookin... though I dinnae know where I'll go.'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 21:59:37 2000] Hagan says, 'If Al'Kabor cannot discover her location through the use of his magic, this Danak must have some powerful friends to help him hide her location.'<br><br>[Mon Oct 02 22:00:04 2000] Thubr Axebringer says, 'He may have th' Ring of Scale helpin' him... that's old magic, lads.  Older than all of us.'

