 his eyes impatiently follow the necromancer's <br>motions.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:41:24 2000] Dartain says, 'Well, perhaps it is time for me to <br>see exactly how worthy of an enemy you truly are.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:41:32 2000] Al`Kabor laughs at Dartain.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:42:27 2000] Dartain feels the favor of the gods upon them.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:42:35 2000] Dartain is cloaked in a shimmer of glowing <br>symbols.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:42:39 2000] Dartain shouts, 'Foolish Wizard! Do you honestly <br>believe that your power, limited by the constraints of this realm could <br>possibly match and agent of Fear?'<br><br><br>(BIG BATTLE)<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:44:52 2000] Dartain chuckles.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:45:04 2000] Dagda Icefury fears for the life of her friend.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:45:34 2000] Al`Kabor shouts, 'You have not the ability to <br>defeat me on your own, Dartain!  Using the might of another to aid your <br>battle is dishonorable beyond all comparison!  This is not the last time <br>that you and I will meet!!'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:45:53 2000] Dartain says, 'Well it appears that my comrades <br>worry themselves too much.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:46:04 2000] Dartain chuckles.<br><br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:46:27 2000] Psalia says, 'I am sorry milord, but I would <br>guard your life this eve.'<br><br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:47:05 2000] Dartain says, 'I wish to thank you for your <br>assistance, Psalia Faute in this great cause of ours.'<br><br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:47:52 2000] Psalia says, 'Whatever assistance I was able to <br>render, you were most welcome to it.'<br><br><br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:49:03 2000] Dartain says, 'You have proven yourself to me to <br>have enormous power, and great potential. If this was a different time, I <br>might have considered taking you as a pupil.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:49:09 2000] Dartain beams a smile at Psalia.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:49:19 2000] Psalia looks crestfallen.<br><br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:50:23 2000] Dartain says, 'There is something I wish for you <br>to have, Psalia Faute, as a symbol of my personal gratitude for your <br>efforts. It shall aid you in your coming ventures throughout this dangerous, <br>wonderous world of ours.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:51:11 2000] Dartain gracefully takes of the first layer of <br>his thick, earthen stained robe. Folding it carefully within his hands, <br>Dartain looks approvingly upon Psalia.<br><br><br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:53:14 2000] Dartain says, 'Since the creation of our first <br>city, deep within the crater of the great magical battle that took place <br>between Erudin and those deemed Heretics, those who lead the Dark Truth were <br>bestowed this artifact of great power.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:53:28 2000] Dartain beams a smile at Psalia.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:54:02 2000] Dartain says, 'I wore this robe the day my fate <br>was sealed behind our own invention that caged the creatures of the <br>Underfoot.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:55:40 2000] Dartain says, 'Strangely enough, the earth of the <br>Underfoot melded their own powerful properties to that of this robe, each <br>thread made from fiber grown within the very realm of fear.'<br>[<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:56:13 2000] Dartain says, 'Psalia Faute, I wish for you to <br>adorn the very small piece of this ancient, distorted artifact.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:56:17 2000] An ancient artifact passes from Dartain of the <br>Dark Truth to Psalia Faute.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:56:45 2000] Dartain says, 'For now, I must depart. Perhaps <br>our paths shall cross again under lighter circumstances.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:57:45 2000] Dagda Icefury shouts, 'Thank you all for your <br>help in defeating the elemental lord!'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:57:54 2000] Anora reaches down and touches the cool earth. <br>The ground still breathes, still lives, The Hole still threatens.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:58:25 2000] Dagda Icefury shouts, 'Anora, you have fought <br>valiantly in the name of good and protection of these fair lands!'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:58:42 2000] Psalia tells the guild, 'thanks everyone for <br>coming =)'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:59:08 2000] Anora says, 'i shall record your names along with <br>those of my companions in my journals'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:59:23 2000] Dagda Icefury says, 'In fair memory of our friend <br>and companion, Firiona Vie, I bestow to you this item of our thanks'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:00:28 2000] Dagda Icefury says, 'My friends, I am so weary <br>this eve, it has indeed been a long day and a battle well fought'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:01:03 2000] Dabner Drednever says, 'Good eve Anora!'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:01:12 2000] Dagda Icefury says, 'We feared that the darkness <br>would ruin us all... but you have saved this land!'<br>[Mon Jun 26 23:01:13 2000] Dabner Drednever waves goodbye to Anora.<br>[Mon Jun 26 23:01:30 2000] Dagda Icefury says, 'Fare thee well my friends, <br>and keep each other safe'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:01:38 2000] Dagda Icefury says, 'You are in good company!'<br><br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:03:48 2000] Dannis says, 'read the stats before they go nuts'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:04:18 2000] Psalia tells the guild, '20ac 20int 12dex 13 <br>svsPoison 100mana and effect gather shadows ( necro invis)'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:04:23 2000] Anora says, 'Chipped Opal Amulet 3ac 15 magic <br>cold poison'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:04:44 2000] Psalia drops in a dead faint.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:05:30 2000] Psalia says, 'I have never even seen a GM event <br>happen before tonight. This was great =)'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 23:05:58 2000] Vladde tells the guild, 'whats its exact name <br>psalia?'

