<P>
<b>Newbiean Rhapsody, to the tune of Bohemian Rhapsody by Queen<br>written by Aedar of Erollisi Marr</b><br> <br>First off, I'd like to tell everyone about how I pronounce certain words, just in case others pronounce them differently. SoW to me is pronounced like "so", char is "care" and exp is of course, "e-x-p". I suggest if you have the song Bohemian Rhapsody you listen you it while you read this so you can appreciate the song more. Enjoy!<br> <br> <br>This is my real life<br>It ain't just fantasy<br>I'm not going back to <br>That place called Reality<br>Open my eyes, look up to my screen and see...<br>I'm just a newbie<br>Please give me your money...<br>Because I'm not too good, level low<br>Please can you spare some dough?<br>Anywhere this char goes doesn't really matter to me...<br>To me...<br> <br>Hey all, just killed a bat<br>Smacked it with my club upside its head<br>Cast my Strike spell, now it's dead<br>Hey all, life had just begun<br>So who told me to target a guard and press A?<br>Hey all, la la la la!<br>Didn't mean to make you /cry<br>If my corpse isn't found by tomorrow<br>Carry on, carry on, 'cause nothing really matters<br> <br>Too late, my corpse is gone<br>It's hard to find my way <br>In this place called Greater Fay<br>Good-bye, everybody, I've got to go<br>Gonna leave this place behind and visit the next zone<br>Hey all, la la la la! (Where this char goes!)<br>I don't want to die<br>But we all know that it's going to happen...<br><br>(During the guitar solo you can hear sounds of monsters killing the newbie)<br><br>I found the corpse of a high-elf paladin!<br>Big deal! Who cares!<br>Where the heck is my own corpse?!<br>Thunderbolt and lightning<br>Makes it very hard to see!<br>What's the /loc of, (what's the /loc of), what's the /loc of, (what's the /loc of)<br>What's the /loc of the next zone?<br>I want to know!<br>I'm just a newbie, somebody help me!<br>He's just a newbie, he doesn't know anything<br>Spare him some gold so he stops spamming me!<br>Easy come, easy go, will you give me SoW?<br>Bismillah! No! We will not give you SoW!<br>Give me SoW! Bismillah! We will not give you SoW!<br>Give me SoW! Bismillah! We will not give you SoW!<br>Give me SoW! Will not give you SoW! Give me SoW! Will not give you SoW!<br>Oh gimme SoW! No, no, no, no, no, NO, NO!!!<br>O kind shaman! O kind druid! Will you please give me SoW?<br>I need a SoW for my corpse recovery...so please...help me!<br><br>So you think you can /ignore me in front of my eyes?<br>I'm going to train something to you and watch you die!<br>Yeah, duel me, I don't care if you duel me<br>I'm just gonna zone out, just gonna zone right out of here!<br><br>Nothing really matters,<br>I don't lose exp<br>Nothing really matters,<br>Nothing really matters...<br>To newbies...<br> <br>Anywhere this char goes...

